屋<br />\n<br />\n但佢地一樣輸比我嘅上進心"},{"pid":"2f88c9adec8d164109d355278d31b9200f2286eb","tid":894372,"uid":86509,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ffc448c07e7604a247065d162dad5be9d38f123e","tid":894372,"uid":78143,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:00:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TXyrb3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTXyrb3f.jpg&h=f317c573&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:10:11.000Z","msg":"第一次睇，最慘好多真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d9a7e552102f86b7d8977f61224498621bf810","tid":894372,"uid":86509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bf0db638212061faca4b641bd2fabe431ab3cd97","tid":894372,"uid":49197,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T11:45:46.000Z","msg":"都唔係無道理...包括我在內識得好多FD知道自己屋企有返咁上下都會減低上進動力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:12:28.000Z","msg":"使乜上進動力，壓榨員工上進咪得囉"},{"pid":"0608752fbcf5fdaf32fa17dfd600f0e679233e6d","tid":894372,"uid":52816,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:12:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"252a181bd0b85f7cead6f9cf94f4ce2e0f44f608","tid":894372,"uid":52816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:13:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"980884a521d37de19625e5a8cb6242a3f179a010","tid":894372,"uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:14:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">動力呀！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/25/214850_088e5cbe5691f2e64c2a73a831246722.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F25%2F214850_088e5cbe5691f2e64c2a73a831246722.gif&h=8dae661d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99961ac5b61f26254af86b01e4f77456c787872a","tid":894372,"uid":56212,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-